{"tid":1855263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小知識: 有關測試陽性 / 陰性","createTime":"2020-02-01T03:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T04:06:58.000Z","uid":323700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"13071c0f9e5d7ab7719d3ffba9ad3ddba10b26e5","tid":1855263,"uid":323700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T03:58:04.000Z","msg":"近來有好多針對今次肺炎 一時陰一時陽 既言論<br />\n為左令大家唔好太擔心, 想貼一貼呢個網址:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/lab/rt-pcr-detection-instructions.html#rRT-PCR-assays\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fcoronavirus%2F2019-ncov%2Flab%2Frt-pcr-detection-instructions.html%23rRT-PCR-assays&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Ii%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=3c70c878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/lab/rt-pcr-detection-instructions.html#rRT-PCR-assays</a><br />\n呢個係來自CDC美國疾病管制與預防中心, 針對今次肺炎既一個檢測流程<br />\n入面用到Real-time RT-PCR 來檢驗病毒既基因<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tTswkrs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtTswkrs.jpg&h=3e0e43b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果三隻assay都中曬 = 陽性<br />\n三隻都唔中 = 陰性<br />\n有種情況就係可能只中一種 / 只中兩種, 呢類型結果會定義為 &quot;inconclusive&quot;<br />\n都需要重新檢測<br />\n<br />\n另外, 由於病毒係身體既量都會隨住時間變化<br />\n或者有機會一開頭抽唔到, 而導致有&quot;假陰性&quot;, 或者初期陰性既問題<br />\n有可能重做, 或隨一段時間再做就有機會變返陽性<br />\n所以其實唔存在著一時陰一時陽既講法<br />\n<br />\n*頭盔: 如果發現有講錯既地方歡迎指正, 或分享你既睇法"},{"pid":"bdfc519a8f8d5815a0263209a6110e3c6c6b2a76","tid":1855263,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T04:00:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78435580e58cde94efce6b4f7dbae9223e32e6de","tid":1855263,"uid":147453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T04:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}